item.title: Google Chrome for Linux Beta
item.description:
This is post is now quite old and the the information it contains may be out of date or innacurate.

If you find any errors or have any suggestions to update the information please let us know or create a pull request on GitHub

Just installed Google Chrome for Linux (Beta), so I could check out this pure CSS3 ATAT (requires a webkit browser). http://anthonycalzadilla.com/css3-ATAT/index.html

Chrome seems to work fine, nice :)
